 Q  The  answer  must  be  a  situation  when  the  number  of  clients  for  the  surgeon 's  service  decreases ,  which  is  a  common  situation  when  people  don 't  want  to  do  something .  Reduction  is  a  service  that  the  surgeon  provides ,  but  it  is  not  the  reason  why  the  number  of  clients  decreases .  Make  larger  and  augment  are  not  the  reasons  why  the  number  of  clients  decreases .  Gain  weight  and  expand  are  not  the  reasons  why  the  number  of  clients  decreases .  Girls  no  longer  want  to  have  the  reduction  surgery ,  which  is  why  the  number  of  clients  for  the  surgeon 's  service  decreases .  So  the  answer  is  have  ( a ).  

