 Q  The  answer  must  be  a  reason  that  can  cause  a  person  to  wake  up  multiple  times  throughout  the  night .  Irr it ability  is  a  feeling  that  can  cause  a  person  to  wake  up ,  but  not  the  reason  for  waking  up .  Depression  is  a  mental  health  condition  that  can  cause  a  person  to  wake  up  multiple  times  throughout  the  night .  Getting  out  of  bed  is  not  a  reason  for  waking  up .  Happiness  is  not  a  reason  for  waking  up .  Dis comfort  is  a  feeling  that  can  cause  a  person  to  wake  up ,  but  not  the  reason  for  waking  up .  What  is  on  your  mind  is  a  common  reason  for  a  person  to  wake  up  multiple  times  throughout  the  night .  So  the  answer  is  depression  ( b ).

 Q  The  answer  must  be  a  situation  where  understanding  the  past  helps  Jesse  with  something  he  is  doing .  Ph oning  is  not  related  to  understanding  the  past .  N ost alg ia  is  a  feeling  that  is  not  directly  related  to  understanding  the  past .  Writing  down  is  a  way  to  record  the  past ,  but  not  directly  related  to  understanding  it .  Active  is  a  state ,  not  a  specific  action .  Being  prepared  is  a  state ,  not  a  specific  action .  Understanding  the  past  helps  Jesse  with  being  prepared  for  the  future ,  so  the  answer  is  being  prepared  ( e ).

 Q  The  answer  must  be  a  place  where  slo ths  are  typically  found .  A  manual  is  not  a  place .  Work  is  not  a  place .  Transit  is  not  a  place .  Coun tryside  is  a  general  place ,  but  slo ths  are  typically  found  in  tropical  jung les .  So  the  answer  is  tropical  jungle  ( a ).

 Q  The  answer  must  be  a  place  where  people  usually  work  on  important  work  assignments .  An  office  building  is  a  common  place  for  people  to  work  on  important  work  assignments .  An  internet  cafe  is  a  place  where  people  can  work  on  their  assignments  but  not  necessarily  important  work  assignments .  A  house  is  a  place  where  people  can  work  on  their  assignments ,  but  not  necessarily  important  work  assignments .  School  is  a  place  where  people  can  work  on  their  assignments ,  but  not  necessarily  important  work  assignments .  So  the  answer  is  office  building  ( a ).

